features.text:
#### Welcome to the wwwwwwwwwwindows exhibition!

The artwork on display is inspired by the one and only John Karel.

This exhibit is a celebration of a phenomenon by the hic et nunc community where lots of users made their own take on John's windows. Those that were collected by John are on display, and all the art is on a 30 second timer.

**If you click on any of the skulls, the artwork will toggle to show John's original artwork (we are in the "scripting" neighborhood afterall!).**
